{"id":"daily-33-the-community-garden","slug":"daily-33-the-community-garden","title":"The Community Garden","title_ko":"함께 가꾸는 정원","level":"B1","ageBand":"8-10","coverUrl":"/seed/daily-33-the-community-garden/cover.webp","summary_ko":"동네 사람들이 함께 정원을 만들며 역할 분담, 협동, 결과를 더 풍부한 문장으로 익혀요.","wordCount":333,"stage":5,"collection":"daily","pages":[{"id":"daily-33-the-community-garden-p1","pageNo":1,"spread":"p1","imageUrl":"/seed/daily-33-the-community-garden/p1.webp","sentences":[{"id":"daily-33-the-community-garden-p1-s1","ord":0,"text":"Our neighborhood decides to make an empty lot into a community garden.","translation_ko":"우리 동네는 빈터를 함께 가꾸는 정원으로 만들기로 해요.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-33-the-community-garden/audio/p1-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Our","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":800},{"word":"neighborhood","charStart":4,"charEnd":16,"startMs":800,"endMs":1240},{"word":"decides","charStart":17,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1240,"endMs":1640},{"word":"to","charStart":25,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1640,"endMs":1840},{"word":"make","charStart":28,"charEnd":32,"startMs":1840,"endMs":1920},{"word":"an","charStart":33,"charEnd":35,"startMs":1920,"endMs":2180},{"word":"empty","charStart":36,"charEnd":41,"startMs":2180,"endMs":2380},{"word":"lot","charStart":42,"charEnd":45,"startMs":2380,"endMs":2700},{"word":"into","charStart":46,"charEnd":50,"startMs":2700,"endMs":2980},{"word":"a","charStart":51,"charEnd":52,"startMs":2980,"endMs":3160},{"word":"community","charStart":53,"charEnd":62,"startMs":3160,"endMs":3500},{"word":"garden","charStart":63,"charEnd":69,"startMs":3500,"endMs":3780}]},{"id":"daily-33-the-community-garden-p1-s2","ord":1,"text":"Everyone agrees it is a wonderful idea, and we cannot wait to begin.","translation_ko":"모두가 훌륭한 생각이라고 동의하며 빨리 시작하고 싶어 해요.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-33-the-community-garden/audio/p1-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Everyone","charStart":0,"charEnd":8,"startMs":0,"endMs":540},{"word":"agrees","charStart":9,"charEnd":15,"startMs":540,