-s2","ord":1,"text":"It does not look like a garden at all, but we stay hopeful.","translation_ko":"전혀 정원처럼 보이지 않지만, 우리는 희망을 잃지 않아요.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-33-the-community-garden/audio/p2-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"It","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":680},{"word":"does","charStart":3,"charEnd":7,"startMs":680,"endMs":900},{"word":"not","charStart":8,"charEnd":11,"startMs":900,"endMs":1200},{"word":"look","charStart":12,"charEnd":16,"startMs":1200,"endMs":1380},{"word":"like","charStart":17,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1380,"endMs":1540},{"word":"a","charStart":22,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1540,"endMs":1900},{"word":"garden","charStart":24,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1900,"endMs":1900},{"word":"at","charStart":31,"charEnd":33,"startMs":1900,"endMs":2180},{"word":"all","charStart":34,"charEnd":37,"startMs":2180,"endMs":2380},{"word":"but","charStart":39,"charEnd":42,"startMs":2660,"endMs":3140},{"word":"we","charStart":43,"charEnd":45,"startMs":3140,"endMs":3340},{"word":"stay","charStart":46,"charEnd":50,"startMs":3340,"endMs":3580},{"word":"hopeful","charStart":51,"charEnd":58,"startMs":3580,"endMs":3900}]},{"id":"daily-33-the-community-garden-p2-s3","ord":2,"text":"We know that with effort, it can become something beautiful.","translation_ko":"노력하면 이 공간이 아름다운 곳으로 변할 수 있다는 걸 알아요.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-33-the-community-garden/audio/p2-s3.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"We","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":240},{"word":"know","charStart":3,"charEnd":7,"startMs":240,"endMs":500},{"word":"that","charStart":8,"charEnd":12,"startMs":500,"endMs":760},{"word":"with","charStart":13,"charEnd":17,"startMs":760,"endMs":1020},{"word":"effort","charStart":18,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1020,"endMs":1280},{"word":"it","charStart":26,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1640,"endMs":1640},{"word":"can","charStart":29,"charEnd":32,"startMs":1640,"endMs":1800},{"word":"become","charStart":33,"charEnd":39,"startMs":1800,"endMs":2080},{"word":"something","charStart":40,"charEnd":49,"